rouletta
========

What is rouletta?
-----------------
rouletta is a simple script, written in python, which tells you
how much money you have to bet in European Roulette, until you
are broke.

Important: never forget the [gambler's fallacy][fallacy]! The
entire risk is with you!


Install & Run
-------------
Just download rouletta.py, install python 2.5 (or higher) and
run rouletta.py in your command line interpreter.

[fallacy]:http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gambler%27s_fallacy
